## New `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Django
db.sqlite3
*.sqlite3
local_settings.py

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
*.env
devsbank.env

# Logs
*.log

# Static and media build artifacts
staticfiles/
media/

# Python packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Testing and coverage
.coverage
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# VS Code
.vscode/

# JetBrains
.idea/

# Misc
*.swp
*.swo